name: Swipeablecard
tagline: A simple implementation of swipe card like StreetView
body:
### Welcome to Swipeable Card Pages.
This is Android Library with implement CardView like StreetView!!

### Authors and Contributors
You can @michelelacorte a GitHub username to generate a link to their profile. The resulting `<a>` element will link to the contributor’s GitHub Profile.
Copyright 2016 Michele Lacorte.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out our [documentation](http://michelelacorte.github.io/SwipeableCard/docs/javadoc/index.html) or [developer page](https://github.com/michelelacorte) to contact us and we’ll help you sort it out.
